## Funnel Analysis Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the funnel: Map every step from entry to conversion
- [ ] 2. Measure drop-off: Calculate conversion rates between each step
- [ ] 3. Identify the biggest leaks: Where is the most significant user loss?
- [ ] 4. Diagnose causes: Why are users dropping at each stage?
- [ ] 5. Generate hypotheses: What changes might improve conversion?
- [ ] 6. Prioritize: Rank fixes by impact and effort
- [ ] 7. Recommend: Specific changes backed by data

